=== EVENT_NEBULA_PHENOMENON ===
# id: 23
# title: Nebula Phenomenon
# chinese_title: 星云现象
# category: Discovery
# mode: starmap

Inside a dense nebula, you witness a natural phenomenon: crystalline structures forming spontaneously from ionized gas.

* [Harvest the crystals]
  ~ gain_scrap(15)
  水晶 (shuǐjīng) — crystal
* [Study the formation process]
  ~ gain_radical("石")
  观察 (guānchá) — observe
* [Pass through quickly — nebulae can be unpredictable]
  ~ lose_fuel(2)
  星云 (xīngyún) — nebula
